records.nl_statement: Show that if $X$ has a countable dense subset, every collection of disjoint open sets in $X$ is countable.
records.lean_header:
import Mathlib

open Filter Set TopologicalSpace
open scoped Topology

  (h : ∃ (s : Set X), Countable s ∧ Dense s) (U : Set (Set X))

  (hUopen : ∀ (u : Set X), u ∈ U → IsOpen u) :
  Countable U :=
